application name configured here

----------------
micronaut:
  application:
    name: learn


we can configure server by adding server part-
    micronaut:
      application:
        name: learn
      server:
        port: 8098
    we can also use place holder
        port:${SERVER_PORT} // then we need to add in system enviorment
        port:${SERVER_PORT:8081}// 8081 fallback value


        we  can set the of server port in the enviorment values



